<img src="http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/discussion/avatars/2010/08/23/downsman/b4c04ae9-9be1-43ef-bfff-e516941e0890/60x60.png" height="60" width="60" alt="" />
<a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/discussion/user/downsman" title="User profile page">downsman</a>

                            
